headline: Young Women in Illinois Rev Up to Build, Race Electric Vehicles in ComEd’s EV Rally
summary: CHICAGO, July 24, 2025--Forty-five young women are gearing up for ComEd’s third EV Rally, a program designed to educate female students on electric vehicles (EVs), science, technology, engineering and math (STEM) principles and the future of clean energy while connecting with female ComEd mentors.
